agent.label: Agent App
descriptions: Manage on the 'Agents' page, allowing individual views of the application to be pinned for use on the 'Workbench'.
Powered by a large language model, it autonomously uses tools, queries data, and builds workflows based on natural language requirements.
Strong generalization capability, requires minimal pre-configured information, but execution may not be precise enough.
Shares a streaming conversation interface consistent with OpenAI's standard API.

workflow.label: Workflow App
descriptions: Manage on the 'Workflow' page, allowing individual views of the application to be pinned for use on the 'Workbench'.
Centered around pre-configured workflows, which can be used directly or invoked by other agent applications.
Strictly executes pre-configured workflows, with stringent input requirements, necessitating background knowledge of the large model during configuration.
Shares input-output API consistent with the configuration.
